  "title": "萤火溪：收集露珠",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "creek",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/forest/forest-02.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "溪水在石头间唱歌，萤火虫把一颗颗露珠照成小灯。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是萤火溪。我们先把“收集露珠”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我闻到了叶子和雨水的味道，森林朋友就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先听树叶的声音，再用温柔的动作帮助这里的朋友。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "collect",
          "prompt": "收集溪边会发光的露珠。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "接住叶尖露珠",
              "feedback": "露珠滚进小瓶子，清凉又明亮。"
            },
            {
              "label": "向萤火虫问路",
              "feedback": "萤火虫带你找到了最大的露珠。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，接住叶尖露珠让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "轻轻完成这一步，藏在叶影里的小路出现了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条小路和森林地图连起来，萤光就会为我们领路。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这片叶子的形状，下一次遇见它就知道该往哪里走。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "‘水’会流动，也会帮助朋友长大。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "right"
        }
      ],
